properties.rdfs:comment: A pointer from a previous, often discontinued variant of the Datagram stream to its newer variant.
properties.rdfs:label: predecessorOf

properties.rdfs:comment: A pointer from a newer variant of a Datagram stream to its previous, often discontinued predecessor.
properties.rdfs:label: successorOf

properties.rdfs:comment: A pointer to a base Datagram stream from which this Datagram stream is a variant. It is safe to infer that the variant inherits all Datagram stream features from the base model, unless defined locally. This is not transitive.
properties.rdfs:label: isVariantOf
